caption:
I could write a letter to describe the reasons why i love Jai Brooks
but he not gonna see it anyway?
so im just going to say that you so much for making my day everyday, for making me smile when im down, for being here with the rest of the boys when no one was, for being here and walking with me through this all shit, you making me smile everyday. Without you, Luke, Daniel, James and Beau - i would give up quicker than you think. I love you so much, thank you for everything.
